Class TextAppInterfaceConnection

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.seagullsw.appinterface.client.BasicAppInterfaceConnection

  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AppInterfaceConnection
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    HTTPAppInterfaceConnection, SocketAppInterfaceConnection

    public abstract class TextAppInterfaceConnection
extends BasicAppInterfaceConnection
    Concrete subclasses use text, usually XML, as the encoding for communication with an AIS.
